Scores ≥3 suggest increased likelihood of severe pancreatitis
Scores < 3 suggest decreased likelihood of severe pancreatitis

Score interpretation:

Score 		Severe Pancreatitis*
0 		7%
1 		6%
2 		16%
3 	 	20%
4 	 	61%
5 	 	55%
6 		100%
7 		0%
8 	 	100%
